com.cognifide.qa.bb.aem.dialog.configurer

Class ComponentConfigBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cognifide.qa.bb.aem.dialog.configurer.ComponentConfigBuilder

  • public class ComponentConfigBuilder
extends Object
    This builder provides a way to construct manually Component Data Tables. Each method creates an ConfigurationEntry matching a single row in the table. To obtain whole config invoke build().
    Entries are added with default tab name: "General". To change it, use setTab(String) method.
